name: The Hell can be beautiful too...

metadata.name: 𝓣𝓱𝓮 𝓗𝓮𝓵𝓵 𝓬𝓪𝓷 𝓫𝓮 𝓫𝓮𝓪𝓾𝓽𝓲𝓯𝓾𝓵...
metadata.description:
In the fiery pits below
Where demons fiercely growl
There lies a beauty untold
The place which we forgot

On the side of my old book-note
I find the address to it
But in fire of Hell, the heat is insane
No one ever survived it. Nor tried it again...
